---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="text-surface transition-colors duration-200 editorial-gradient">
  <div class="w-full px-6 md:px-12 py-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-8 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <span class="text-lg font-bold text-surface block mb-4">Observatório Nacional ETP</span>
      <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 mb-8">
        Iniciativa dedicada à transparência e análise de dados sobre o Ensino Técnico e Profissionalizante no Brasil. Fomentando a inovação educacional através da evidência.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-xs font-label tracking-widest opacity-50 uppercase">Apoio Institucional</p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <a href="https://institutoyduqs.com.br/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-secondary-fixed font-bold hover:text-surface transition-colors">Instituto Yduqs</a>
          <span class="text-white/30">|</span>
          <a href="https://estacio.br/cursos-tecnicos-principais" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-secondary-fixed font-bold hover:text-surface transition-colors">Estácio</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60">Explorar</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/metodologia/">Metodologia</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/glossario/">Glossário</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/imprensa/">Imprensa</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/guia/">Guia de Cursos</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/sobre/">Sobre</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/60">Dados</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/painel/">Painel de Indicadores</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/comparacoes/">Comparações</a></li>
          <li><a class="text-outline-variant hover:text-surface text-sm transition-opacity" href="/politicas/">Políticas Públicas</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 border-t border-white/5 pt-8">
    <p class="font-body text-xs text-outline-variant opacity-60">
      &copy; {currentYear} Observatório Nacional ETP. Todos os direitos reservados.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-6 items-center">
      <span class="font-bold tracking-tighter text-secondary-fixed">Dados Abertos</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
